column17:
Samsung Guru E1207 Black:
Samsung presents Guru E1207 a handy cell phone that boasts of a stylish bar design with curved edges. It is an ideal choice for people who are looking for uncomplicated cell phone experience. This Samsung phone is a dual SIM mobile phone that supports 2 GSM SIMs (one on standby). This feature allows the user to stay connected in more than one way. It is equipped with an alphanumeric keypad to facilitate easy typing. There is an FM radio functionality to keep you entertained on the go.
